steps.name: Click on the 'Clients' link from the sidebar menu
Click on the client name from the table
Click on the 'New policy' link from the client landing page
Select 'Manual input' option for the creation of the new policy
Click on the 'Next' button to continue creating a new policy
Enter the number of the policy into the 'Policy Number' field
Enter carrier name into the search field for the 'Carrier' dropdown
